column2: SELECT input.*, po.ra AS sdss_ra, po.dec AS sdss_dec FROM MyDB.AKARImain_SDSSspecDR1#_bestobjid input INNER JOIN PhotoObjAll po ON po.objid = input.sdss_bestobjid LEFT OUTER JOIN Photoz pz ON pz.objid = input.sdss_bestobjid LEFT OUTER JOIN TwoMassXSC tmass ON tmass.objid = input.sdss_bestobjid LEFT OUTER JOIN FIRST ft ON ft.objid = input.sdss_bestobjid LEFT OUTER JOIN WISE_xmatch wise_mat ON wise_mat.sdss_objid = input.sdss_bestobjid ORDER BY search_id
